---
layout: base.njk
title: Lab Notes | Odderon Lab
description: Engineering lab notes from Odderon Lab. Prototyping insights, hardware design decisions, and embedded system protection techniques.
---

<section class="container page-content">
  <h1>Lab Notes</h1>
  <p>Development updates, engineering notes, and design insights.</p>

  {% for post in collections.posts %}
    {% if not post.data.draft %}
  <article class="blog-post">
    <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
    <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date }}</time>
    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="btn-primary">Read more</a>
  </article>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>